rows.label: qst200420_0010
rows.name: Ugh... Why the hell won't you end this?!

rows.label: qst200420_0020
rows.name:
...I am not a killer.
Not even when it comes to worthless scum like you.

rows.label: qst200420_0030
rows.name:
...Heh heh heh...
Not a killer?

rows.label: qst200420_0040
rows.name: Stop fooling yourself, boyo...

rows.label: qst200420_0050
rows.name:
Even if you don't kill me now,
you can bet your arse someone will...

rows.label: qst200420_0060
rows.name:
...Like that woman.
Everyone dies, sooner or later...

rows.label: qst200420_0070
rows.name: Vasara!

rows.label: qst200420_0080
rows.name:
Your skills... They are made for
ending people's lives!

rows.label: qst200420_0090
rows.name: It's like you don't get it...

rows.label: qst200420_0100
rows.name:
It doesn't matter how many times you're reborn,
a killer is what you are.

rows.label: qst200420_0110
rows.name:
Need proof? That burning desire you feel
to kill me now is proof enough!

rows.label: qst200420_0120
rows.name:
What's wrong?
Do it!

rows.label: qst200420_0130
rows.name:
You hate me, don't you?
You won't let scum like me live, will you?!

rows.label: qst200420_0140
rows.name:
You can stop holding back
and kill me already, Vasara!

rows.label: qst200420_0150
rows.name: Do it, and reclaim your past glory!

rows.label: qst200420_0160
rows.name: ...I will not.

rows.label: qst200420_0170
rows.name:
Dying here would be too easy
an end for one such as you.

rows.label: qst200420_0180
rows.name:
No, you will live, so that you can spend
the rest of your life atoning for your sins.

rows.label: qst200420_0190
rows.name:
That... Isn't that a fate
crueler than death...?

rows.label: qst200420_0200
rows.name: Vasara, you really are the Heartless Judge...
